ang tersedia di menu Assets ? hal ini sangat berguna untuk pendataan jumlah buku yang tersedia di perusahaan, terimakasih','new',NULL,'[\"feedback/019c1c6c-79c1-77ed-a5b8-1a5f68b2af71.png\"]'),(25,1,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-02 17:03:55.872642','2026-02-02 17:03:55.872642',NULL,'019c1dcf-1253-75d9-a85e-4286f3cb51f8',1,'keluhan','testing','new',NULL,'[\"feedback/019c1dcf-123c-7211-b03d-5632f5092b3f.png\"]'),(26,1,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-02 17:08:47.028164','2026-02-02 17:08:47.028164',NULL,'019c1dd3-83a7-71cd-a72e-88c2fd89ab77',1,'saran','tes','new',NULL,'[\"feedback/019c1dd3-8388-704a-bb72-2a2629e0821d.png\",\"feedback/019c1dd3-839c-761c-9973-93346c54a510.webp\"]'),(27,7,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-02 17:35:45.333117','2026-02-02 17:35:45.333117',NULL,'019c1dec-352a-72ce-ab43-99faa600b717',7,'keluhan','Saat tambahkan foto ke asset terjadi eror saat upload fotonya, mohon bantu dicek ya, terimakasih\r\n\r\nlink rekam layar : \r\nhttps://jam.dev/c/17535667-bd3b-43aa-a859-523fd015fd26','new',NULL,'[\"feedback/019c1dec-350d-710d-9590-c827294624e8.png\"]');
